I have started a new forum on the Cantera sourceforge site to discuss 
issues related to the Cantera C++ kernel and C++ Cantera applications.
Anyone can read the messages, and if you have a sourceforge username 
you can post messages.  You can also subscribe to this forum, so that 
you receive by email each posted message (much like this mailing list).

One outcome of the Cantera Developer's meeting held last Monday is that 
we plan to make more use of features of sourceforge.  Other forums may 
be established on other topics.
